Package com.wounit.rules

This package contains JUnit MethodRule implementations to be used while unit testing WebObjects applications.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractEditingContextRule
    AbstractEditingContextRule is a subclass of ERXEC that implements the MethodRule interface.
    MockEditingContext
    MockEditingContext is a subclass of AbstractEditingContextRule that provides means for fast in-memory testing of EOEnterpriseObjects.
    TemporaryEditingContext
    The TemporaryEditingContext class provides means to create temporary enterprise object for unit testing.
